data.description: Opportunity awaits!! A great home for a first-time home buyer or a seasoned investor.  This spacious 3 BR, 1.5 BA home was completely rehabbed via the Neighborhood Stabilization program. You're welcomed by a dreamy wrap around porch and views of the Ohio river. This home offers a large eat-in kitchen, dining room and light filled living room. 3 spacious bedrooms and full bath complete the 2nd floor. Stairs to the partially finished attic add additional potential for a bonus room or loft. A generous flat backyard leads to off street parking with ally access. Energy Star appliances and eco-friendly construction methods were previously used to rehab this home. This well-loved home needs some cosmetic repairs including paint and new carpet and retaining wall, but price is reflected accordingl Sold as is. Schedule your private showing today!
